All documentation for ECATools can be found at:

https://github.com/rhysf/ECATools

Entirely Covered in All (ECA) Tools is a pipeline for extracting phylogenetically
informative sites from several VCFs. 

Prerequisites:
--------------

Perl
Bio-Perl
Python

Getting started / example pipeline:
-----------------------------------

git clone https://github.com/rhysf/ECATools.git
cd ECATools/examples/
gunzip *.gz
perl ../ECA_maker.pl -v Name_Type_location.tab -f Cryp_gatt_R265.genome.fa-scaffold3.14.fasta -r 123 -i y -s 1 
perl ../ECA_maker.pl -v Name_Type_location.tab -f Cryp_gatt_R265.genome.fa-scaffold3.14.fasta -r 123 -i y -s 2

Individual script details:
--------------------------

ECA-maker.pl
ECA_pull_VCF_positions.pl
